cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about sentiment analysis using deep learning techniques, specifically convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves machine learning and neural networks, which suggests that it could also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (IR) techniques, which could place it under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which could place it under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
